      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2025-03-10</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2025-06-23T12:11:04Z</updateDate>
        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sanction Sea Pirates Act of 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill requires the President to impose visa- and property-blocking sanctions on any foreign person (individual or entity) that the President determines knowingly engages in piracy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill also applies civil and criminal penalties to persons that violate, attempt to violate, conspire to violate, or cause a violation of&amp;nbsp;the regulations promulgated to carry out such sanctions.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
